name: My-Mp3-Cutter
descriptionHTML: This is a simple MP3 Cutter Application which can cut a specific part of an audio file. You can also append one song after another and set the newly created files as ringtone for specific contact, notification,alarm or default ringtone. It contains banner ads. This project was developed by me in my free time just for practice. It is an attempt to clone this application: http://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.betteridea.ringtone.mp3.editor
